Articles.Content:
BluPlanet Incorporated presents you the latest in kerbal ground transport, the Ace Rover I. Designed by new rover and plane builder Ace of spades, this vehicle carries 10 passengers and one driver. Let your pilots ride in agony..er I mean comfort!

Download: https://www.dropbox.com/s/2q2hb48yh4zrtdv/Rover%20Ace-1.craft

It has a nice driving IVA!

never walk again

Enjoy! CREDIT: Ace of spades

Ment as a rescue shuttle and shuttle to launch pad

-Ace
